</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ ASTEROIDS ═══════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="asteroids">
  <p class="section-label">The Named Forces</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Key Asteroids</h2>
  <div class="divider"></div>

  <div class="asteroid-grid">
    <div class="asteroid-card">
      <div class="asteroid-name">Hekate (100)</div>
      <div class="asteroid-pos">18°17' · 8th House</div>
      <div class="asteroid-meaning">Magic, intuition, shadow work. The goddess of crossroads holds court in the house of death and rebirth.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="asteroid-card">
      <div class="asteroid-name">Cleopatra (216)</div>
      <div class="asteroid-pos">21°35' · 8th House · Stationary</div>
      <div class="asteroid-meaning">Royalty, seduction, sovereign power. Stationary — immovable, permanent, impossible to ignore. Activated by Libra lunations.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="asteroid-card">
      <div class="asteroid-name">Kali (4227)</div>
      <div class="asteroid-pos">21°36' · 1st House</div>
      <div class="asteroid-meaning">Destruction and rebirth as identity. One degree from Cleopatra — the destroyer and the queen occupying the same breath.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="asteroid-card">
